\begin_layout Enumerate
Verify that
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
u(x,t)=\frac{1}{2c}\int_{x-ct}^{x+ct}g(\xi)d\xi
\]

\end_inset

is a solution to the PDE 
\begin_inset Formula $u_{tt}=c^{2}u_{xx}$
\end_inset

 where 
\begin_inset Formula $c$
\end_inset

 is a constant and 
\begin_inset Formula $g$
\end_inset

