\begin_layout Itemize
A conversation law is just a mathematical formulation of the basic fact
 that the rate at which a quantity changes in a given domain must equal
 rate at which quantity flows across the boundary plus the rate which quantity
 is created
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
State variable 
\begin_inset Formula $u(x,t)$
\end_inset

