\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

, at time 
\begin_inset Formula $t$
\end_inset

 which measures the amount of quantity crossing section 
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

 at time 
\begin_inset Formula $t$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Source term 
\begin_inset Formula $f(x,t)$
\end_inset

