\begin_inset Formula 
\[
u_{t}+\Phi_{x}(\mu)=u_{t}+\Phi'(u)u_{x}=0
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
If 
\begin_inset Formula $\Phi(u)$
\end_inset

 is not linear in 
